Class DominantOrientationExtractor

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FeatureVectorExtractor<FloatFV,GradientScaleSpaceImageExtractorProperties<FImage>>

    public class DominantOrientationExtractor
extends AbstractDominantOrientationExtractor
    Extract the dominant orientations of a scale-space interest point by looking for peaks in its orientation histogram.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)

    • Field Detail

      • DEFAULT_PEAK_THRESHOLD

        public static float DEFAULT_PEAK_THRESHOLD
        Default value for the threshold at which other peaks are detected relative to the biggest peak. Lowe's IJCV paper suggests a value of 80%.

      • oriHistExtractor

        protected OrientationHistogramExtractor oriHistExtractor

      • peakThreshold

        protected float peakThreshold
        Threshold for peak detection. A value of 1.0 would result in only a single peak being detected.
